<wfauthor>By Chris Whitaker</wfauthor>
<wfdescription>&lt;p&gt;This is a Group Work Lesson Script to actively engage students with course material within an online format. This script can serve as a helpful guide to engage students using a flipped classroom design that gets students doing pre-class
work, engages them in small-group work during class, and follows up with a post class activity.&lt;/p&gt;</wfdescription>
