<column>OOCI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Prepare and assign material (text, video, etc.) for students to review before synchronous class.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Z7dWD4DjDs" target="_blank"&gt;Moodle &lt;/a&gt;easily allows reflections to be done on-line&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?reload=9&amp;amp;v=yaGL0oQ2u9M&amp;amp;t=0s&amp;amp;ab_channel=SALTISE" target="_blank"&gt;MyDALITE &lt;/a&gt;easily allows reflections to be done on-line but it adds a component of interactivity that allows students to see and reflect on each otherâ€™s reflections&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Both Moodle and MyDALITE also allow you to add multiple choice questions to the reflections&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
<linkedwf>undefined</linkedwf>
<textheight>260</textheight>
<isdropped>true</isdropped>
</node>
