<righticon>reading</righticon>
<column>OOC</column>
<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Review the assigned material, without formally studying it&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Write reflections on the things that were confusing/difficult, using the detailed &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/190BMM992xC4cigkxgQhd1uhU5K4RV75f3mJ8H5iQusc/edit?usp=drive_open&amp;amp;ouid=114858286146124777919" target="_blank"&gt;Reflective Writing Instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Submit the written reflection&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
<linkedwf>undefined</linkedwf>
<textheight>150</textheight>
