<lefticon>undefined</lefticon>
<righticon>undefined</righticon>
<column>OOCI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Review a sub-set of the reflection submissions and use this to guide the preparation for the online class. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: Refer to this &lt;a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1eh_a5Al8lFDvBwQa7DNSgoMoFRjkyt-q/view" target="_blank"&gt;example&lt;/a&gt; of how you might use reflections to start your in-class mini-lecture.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
