<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Begin your class with a review of student reflections&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Give a mini lecture that addresses with what students found confusing/difficult&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
