<column>ICI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Explain and specify:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;what you want students to do&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;what artifact you want them to generate (i.e. Google doc, scanned sketches etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;how much time they have&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;Split students in groups and monitor as they work.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
