<id>9</id>
<lefticon>undefined</lefticon>
<righticon>orchestration</righticon>
<column>ICI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Review the task(s) along with the student generated artifacts&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;End the online class by consolidating what you want them to take away from the activity&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jsnswNCx334" target="_blank"&gt;See how Zoom&lt;/a&gt; easily allows for the creation of breakout rooms where students can talk, use the chat and write on a shared canvas&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FAYwXW7R8V8" target="_blank"&gt;See how Span&lt;/a&gt; easily allows students to work on a shared canvas that is dynamic and accessed through a web browser&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
