<column>ICI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Provide students with proper notes/ solutions so that there are no mistaken ideas/elements from the group work that you might have missed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Moodle easily allows this to be done on-line and then Mio or email can be used for the following student reflections and instructor feedback steps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ODE6v4YOo0E" target="_blank"&gt;See how Perusall&lt;/a&gt; allows this step to be done on-line in a dynamic and interactive way. Post PDF versions of documents on Perusall and have students collectively annotate them. Students can even help each other, and the instructor gets to see and manage it all through a web browser or Moodle module&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
